### Component 8: Code Wiring

#### [MODIFY] [rewriter.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py)

**B1. Research Sections:**
```python
_POV_RESEARCH_SECTION_A = {
    "name": "Core Identity & Timeline",
    "fields": ["core_topic", "age_timeline", "life_phases"],
    "prompt_focus": "..."
}
_POV_RESEARCH_SECTION_B = {
    "name": "Key Events & Turning Points", 
    "fields": ["key_events", "turning_points", "key_relationships"],
    "prompt_focus": "..."
}
_POV_RESEARCH_SECTION_C = {
    "name": "Physical Arc & Death",
    "fields": ["physical_state_arc", "death_scene", "legacy"],
    "prompt_focus": "..."
}
_RESEARCH_SECTIONS_POV = [_POV_RESEARCH_SECTION_A, _POV_RESEARCH_SECTION_B, _POV_RESEARCH_SECTION_C]
```

**B2. Dispatch Maps** — thêm POV keywords vào TẤT CẢ dispatch maps:
```python
# In _get_research_sections():
"pov":           _RESEARCH_SECTIONS_POV,
"pov_tiểu_sử":  _RESEARCH_SECTIONS_POV,
"pov biography": _RESEARCH_SECTIONS_POV,
"pov_biography": _RESEARCH_SECTIONS_POV,

# In _NICHE_PROMPT_MAP and all narrative dispatch maps:
"pov":           "system_narrative_write_pov.txt",  # writer
"pov_tiểu_sử":  "system_narrative_write_pov.txt",
# ... same pattern for outline, phase_plan, audit, review
```

**B3. Niche Detection:**
```python
_is_pov = any(k in _niche_lower for k in ("pov", "pov_tiểu_sử", "pov_biography", "level"))

# In _extract_chapter_blueprint():
elif _is_pov:
    chapter_bp = _extract_chapter_blueprint(...)  # fuzzy search, lightweight
    
# Hook strategy:
elif _is_pov:
    chapter_bp = _extract_chapter_blueprint(...)  # Filtered (lean) like battle

# In write_from_blueprint():
elif _is_pov:
    # Inject age_anchor and physical_state from outline into write prompt
```

**B4. Outline Fields:**
```python
_NICHE_OUTLINE_FIELDS["pov"] = [
    "level_number", "age_anchor", "physical_state",
    "main_key_data", "sub_key_data", "chapter_structure",
    "closing_type", "emotional_beat", "word_count_target"
]
```

**B5. Key Normalization:**
```python
# Add POV-specific key variants:
"age_timeline": "age_timeline",
"physical_state_arc": "physical_state_arc",
"death_scene": "death_scene",
```

> [!CAUTION]
> **ALL changes in rewriter.py MUST use niche branching** (`elif _is_pov:`). 
> NEVER modify existing `_is_biography` or `_is_battle` branches.
> After EVERY change, verify biography + battle v2 still work.

